  <entry>
    <title>Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/10/hyperv/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/10/hyperv/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hyper-v-Ubuntu-折腾日志-leaves"><a href="#Hyper-v-Ubuntu-折腾日志-leaves" class="headerlink" title="Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志:leaves:"></a>Hyper-v + Ubuntu 折腾日志:leaves:</h1><h2 id="安装Hyper-v"><a href="#安装Hyper-v" class="headerlink" title="安装Hyper-v"></a>安装Hyper-v</h2><p>win11家庭版中没有hyper-v，需要新建文本文档输入下面的指令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">pushd</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;%~dp0&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">dir</span> /b %SystemRoot%\servicing\Packages\*Hyper-V*.mum &gt;hyper-v.txt<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> /f %%i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> (<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;findstr /i . hyper-v.txt 2^&gt;nul&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">do</span> dism /online /norestart /add-package:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%SystemRoot%\servicing\Packages\%%i&quot;</span><br>del hyper-v.txt<br>Dism /online /enable-feature /featurename:Microsoft-Hyper-V-All /LimitAccess /ALL<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将文件名修改为hyper-v.cmd（包括后缀名）右键管理员权限运行，等待之后y重启</p><p>设置中搜索控制面板-&gt; 程序 –&gt; 启用或关闭windows的功能</p><p>找到hyper-v, 虚拟机监控, 虚拟机平台打开(可能会重启)</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>hexo折腾日志</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/08/hexo%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/08/hexo%E6%8A%98%E8%85%BE%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <del>咱也没学过html,咱也不敢问</del></p><p>8.5</p><p><strong>url设置:cry:</strong></p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-attr">permalink</span>: :year/:month/:day/:title/<br><span class="hljs-attr">permalink_defaults</span>:<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>改为</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-attr">permalink</span>: post/:abbrlink.<span class="hljs-property">html</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">abbrlink</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">alg</span>: crc32<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">rep</span>: hex<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>就发生了一些奇怪的问题, 点击任何一篇只能链接到同一篇文章,改回来又正常了</p><p>8.11</p><p>今天进行本地生成时发现**Permission denied. You can’t use port 4000.**4000可能被占用了(似乎也没有开其他的进程), 总之就是换一个port就好了</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo s -p 5000<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p><strong>插入图片</strong></p><p>这里还是来一个比较靠谱的教程<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/265077468">hexo博客如何插入图片 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p><p>but</p><p>这些方法我用起来都不太行</p><p>最后只有祭出图床大法才能成功（网址在这里<a href="https://sm.ms/">Image Upload - SM.MS - Simple Free Image Hosting</a>）</p><p>直接登录上传，然后复制md格式粘贴就好了</p><hr><p>一般会遇到<strong>fatal: unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/Reductionreaction/Reductionreaction.github.io.git/">https://github.com/Reductionreaction/Reductionreaction.github.io.git/</a>‘: Recv failure: Connection was reset</strong>这样的报错，需要取消git本身的代理</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">git config --global --<span class="hljs-built_in">unset</span> http.proxy<br><br>git config --global --<span class="hljs-built_in">unset</span> https.proxy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后直接上传或者科学上网就好了</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>奇怪的东西</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>Hello World</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/08/hello-world/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/08/hello-world/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>一些py数据处理工具</title>
    <link href="/2023/08/07/test/"/>
    <url>/2023/08/07/test/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Matplotlib-laughing"><a href="#Matplotlib-laughing" class="headerlink" title="Matplotlib:laughing:"></a>Matplotlib:laughing:</h1><p><del>不能直接上导图我也是没有办法</del></p><p><strong>函数图像</strong></p><p>废话不多说，直接上代码</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#正余弦函数</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> plt<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> math<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> numpy<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#将0-2Π分成100份</span><br>X = numpy.linspace(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>*numpy.pi,<span class="hljs-number">100</span>)<br><br>Y = numpy.sin(X)<br><br>plt.plot(X,Y)<br><br>Y = numpy.cos(X)<br><br>plt.plot(X,Y)<br><br>plt.savefig(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;result2.png&#x27;</span>)<br>plt.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#一般函数</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> plt<br><br>X = <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(-<span class="hljs-number">100</span>,<span class="hljs-number">100</span>)<br><br>Y = [x**<span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> x <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> X]<br><br>plt.plot(X,Y)<br>plt.savefig(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;result1.png&#x27;</span>)<br>plt.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/11/EctlxGuVBIfbyzZ.jpg" alt="result1.jpg" style="zoom:67%;" /><p><strong>绘制统计图</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#条形图</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> plt<br><span class="hljs-comment">#宽度是指标砖宽度的倍数</span><br>plt.bar([<span class="hljs-number">1980</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1985</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1990</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1995</span>],[<span class="hljs-number">1000</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3000</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4000</span>,<span class="hljs-number">5000</span>],width=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)<br>plt.savefig(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;result2.png&#x27;</span>)<br>plt.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/11/AfGpRwaEmk52K1U.png" alt="result2.png" style="zoom:67%;" /><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-comment">#直方图和盒状图</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> plt<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> np<br><br>data = np.random.randn(<span class="hljs-number">100</span>)<br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(data)<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(np.average(data))<br><br>fig,(ax1,ax2) = plt.subplots(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,figsize=(<span class="hljs-number">8</span>,<span class="hljs-number">8</span>))<br><br>ax1.hist(data,<span class="hljs-number">100</span>)<br>ax2.boxplot(data)<br><br>plt.savefig(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;result3.png&#x27;</span>)<br>plt.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/08/11/sMDF1LgbVrCjTim.png" alt="result3.png" style="zoom:67%;" /><p><strong>添加标题</strong></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> plt<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> numpy<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#如果包含中文标题需要写</span><br>plt.rcParams[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;font.sans-serif&#x27;</span>] = [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;SimHei&#x27;</span>]<br><br>X =numpy.linspace(-<span class="hljs-number">4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">4</span>,<span class="hljs-number">1024</span>)<br>Y = <span class="hljs-number">0.25</span>*(X+<span class="hljs-number">4</span>)*(X+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)*(X-<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br><br>plt.title(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;多项式曲线&#x27;</span>)<br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置latex标题需要</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#plt.title(r&#x27;$...$&#x27;)</span><br><br>plt.plot(X,Y,c=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;r&#x27;</span>)<br>plt.show()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Pandas"><a href="#Pandas" class="headerlink" title="Pandas"></a>Pandas</h1><p>这里还是先找一个教程 </p><p><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/99889912">【十分钟Python知识点】pandas最详细教程 - 知乎 (zhihu.com)</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
